The village was built around 450 years ago and the amiki
family was the first family to settle in the village.

176
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:30,000
Gundê Berkaşê li quntarên çiyayê Hawar ku weke bilindtirîn
çiya li herêma Efrînê tê naskirin û asê ye bi taybet ji
aliyê rojava ve hatiye avakirin.
 
The village of Berkash is built at the foot of Mount Hawar,
which is known as the highest mountain in the Afrin region
and is steep, especially on the west side.

177
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:36,000
Tê zanîn ku di sedsala bihorî de bi dehan xelkê herêmê ji
ber zilmê direviyan û diçin vî gundî.
 
It is known that in the last century dozens of people from
the region fled from oppression and went to this village.

178
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:56,000
Ev gund bi huner û dengbêjiyê, û govendê navdar e, û gelek
hunermend ji wan derketine.
 
This village is famous for art, singing, and dancing, and
many artists have emerged from them.

179
