200
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:16,000
Em niha bi dayîkan re qise bikin.
 
Let's talk to the mothers now.

201
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,000
Saet a we xweş.
 
Good job.

202
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:22,000
Dayê merhaba jîn û jiyara min
 
Hello my life and living

203
