Dayê em destpêkê te nas bikin.
 
Mother, let's get to know you first.

205
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:32,000
Ez Xebîbe me, qîza Muhemedî Baso me, ji gundê Kemarê.
 
I am Xebibe, the daughter of Muhamed Baso, from the village
